  "2026-06-21T08:41:01.185Z",codex-impl,"Evidence: implemented least-privilege manifest metadata in generated package/extension scaffolds (trusted=true, sandbox_profile=strict, all declared permissions false), added focused scaffold assertions, and updated SDK/extension author docs. Validation passed: focused linked test 94 tests; pnpm build; pnpm quality:static; pnpm quality:docs-links; pnpm contracts:check; pnpm changelog:pm:check; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage = 241 files / 4796 tests / 100% statements, branches, functions, lines; manual temp-dir package scaffold/install/invoke/npm-test/package-doctor smoke; pm health summary ok; pnpm security:scan; npm pack --dry-run; sentry-telemetry gate ok; pm telemetry status showed successful recent flush; pnpm release:gates passed."
  "2026-06-21T08:47:11.094Z",codex-impl,"Review follow-up: addressed Sourcery/CodeRabbit feedback by cloning scaffold permissions into each generated manifest, aligning generated manifest field ordering with docs, and adding extension-only README policy metadata assertions. Re-validated focused scaffold spec, pnpm build, and pnpm changelog:pm:check."
